ge.hk%2Fphotos%2Fa.621044248395945%2F774178706415831%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZM0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=c10add55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jiegenge.hk/photos/a.621044248395945/774178706415831/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}